<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save global-prefix
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>This is partially based on the code used by npm internally to resolve the global prefix.</p>
